1
00:01:10,680 --> 00:01:11,440
Look at this.

2
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:22,090
King Ling ordered the Xies to kill me long ago.

3
00:01:25,480 --> 00:01:27,320
You met with Xie Yuheng in secret tonight

4
00:01:27,320 --> 00:01:28,200
just for this?

5
00:01:28,880 --> 00:01:29,960
How did you know

6
00:01:30,600 --> 00:01:32,530
that I was meeting with Xie Yuheng?

7
00:01:38,440 --> 00:01:39,880
Someone deliberately had this note

8
00:01:39,880 --> 00:01:41,610
sent to Zhuque Pavilion today.

9
00:01:41,720 --> 00:01:42,920
It must be Yan Mingli.

10
00:01:43,360 --> 00:01:45,620
Yan Mingli often uses such clumsy tricks

11
00:01:45,759 --> 00:01:46,759
to stir up trouble

12
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,340
and watch the show.

13
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:50,460
I have found out the truth.

14
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:52,420
The assassins on your wedding day

15
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:54,680
were neither the Xie family's sword slaves

16
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:56,680
nor King Ling's Black Armor Guards.

17
00:01:57,400 --> 00:01:58,360
On their necks,

18
00:01:59,360 --> 00:02:01,760
they all had Northern Di wolf head tattoos.

19
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:04,060
Only the Northern Di royal guards

20
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:05,820
have such tattoos.

21
00:02:13,440 --> 00:02:16,800
King Ling ordered the Xies to kill me,

22
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:20,360
and they borrowed Northern Di's blade.

23
00:02:23,000 --> 00:02:26,660
What a brilliant scheme to use someone else to do their dirty work.

24
00:02:29,640 --> 00:02:30,570
You're injured.

25
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:35,180
The wound is poisoned.

26
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:09,540
Your Highness.

27
00:03:20,880 --> 00:03:21,610
Good weapon.

28
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:23,440
Your Highness is wise.

29
00:03:23,440 --> 00:03:25,120
The black iron ingots used this time

30
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:26,720
and the top-quality batch from three years ago

31
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:28,050
come from the same vein.

32
00:03:28,480 --> 00:03:30,800
Only after seven times of quenching can we get this sharpness.

33
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,120
Not to mention the enemy's armor,

34
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:33,360
even the best refined steel

35
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:35,600
is like rotten wood before this blade.

36
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:42,410
With these divine weapons,

37
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:44,280
my iron cavalry

38
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:47,090
will surely destroy cities and forts,

39
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:48,480
and be invincible.

40
00:03:48,880 --> 00:03:50,880
Your Highness holding such sharp weapons

41
00:03:50,880 --> 00:03:52,840
is truly the will of heaven.

42
00:03:53,160 --> 00:03:54,680
Hegemony is to be expected,

43
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:56,340
and the world is in your hands.

44
00:04:12,200 --> 00:04:13,160
Miss Yan,

45
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:15,820
can't you be a bit gentler with me?

46
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:18,640
Committing theft

47
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:19,920
is the worst plan.

48
00:04:20,279 --> 00:04:22,410
And you came back covered in injuries.

49
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:27,540
My Lord, there's a situation.

50
00:04:27,760 --> 00:04:28,240
Speak.

51
00:04:28,640 --> 00:04:30,760
The Northern Di scimitars secretly forged by the Prince of Ling have been loaded.

52
00:04:30,760 --> 00:04:34,020
They will be sent to Northern Di tomorrow at the hour of Yin.

53
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:35,900
Keep a close watch.

54
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:37,520
Don't miss a single soldier.

55
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:38,050
Yes, sir.

56
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:44,520
The Prince of Ling uses Xie Yuheng's escort of provisions as a cover.

57
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:45,760
In reality, the provision carts are loaded with

58
00:04:45,760 --> 00:04:47,690
weapons destined for Northern Di.

59
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:49,890
Perfect. We'll catch them all at once.

60
00:04:53,159 --> 00:04:53,920
Bear with it.

61
00:05:02,400 --> 00:05:04,130
Your wounds have been treated.

62
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:06,880
Keep them away from water for a few days.

63
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:09,680
Thank you, Miss Yan,

64
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:12,000
for saving my life again.

65
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:39,460
The fire is too strong.

66
00:05:39,840 --> 00:05:41,170
We need to find a way out.

67
00:05:57,640 --> 00:05:58,370
Are you okay?

68
00:05:58,520 --> 00:05:59,240
I'm fine.

69
00:05:59,840 --> 00:06:00,960
Fire! Hurry!

70
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,320
Hurry! Fire!

71
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:03,800
Fire! Fire!

72
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:04,800
Hurry, put out the fire!

73
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:05,560
Come on!

74
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:09,360
They even resorted to burning the building to destroy evidence.

75
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,120
It seems

76
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:12,810
we've stepped on the tiger's tail.

77
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:13,920
This fire

78
00:06:14,400 --> 00:06:15,600
was set by Xie Yuheng.

79
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:16,760
He...

80
00:06:17,960 --> 00:06:19,560
He is just following orders,

81
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:22,500
a mere executioner killing with a blade.

82
00:07:00,320 --> 00:07:01,520
I woke Linlang up.

83
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:04,340
I was wrong. I should be punished.

84
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:07,880
I'll punish myself by eating this whole bowl of tangyuan.

85
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:12,240
When I came in to bring the tangyuan just now,

86
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:13,400
you were not here.

87
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,800
How did you suddenly, like magic,

88
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:16,400
come back?

89
00:07:16,840 --> 00:07:17,920
Could it be

90
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,680
that in your room,

91
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:22,640
there is a secret passage leading outside?

92
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:24,020
You smart little girl.

93
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:26,320
You've read too much of Women's Virtues,

94
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:27,480
and your little head

95
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:29,080
is all confused.

96
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:31,730
Those rules your mother taught you

97
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:34,760
will only stifle your spirit.

98
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:38,240
My daughter should be like a boy.

99
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:39,760
You should not be confined to the boudoir.

100
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:42,200
You can practice martial arts and study military tactics.

101
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:43,000
In the future,

102
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:51,700
even if I cannot always protect you by your side,

103
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:54,730
you can also rely on your own skills

104
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:56,159
to protect yourself.

105
00:07:58,800 --> 00:08:00,120
Father.

106
00:08:00,960 --> 00:08:02,890
These military tactics and rules,

107
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:04,800
I don't want to learn any of them.

108
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:09,530
Alright.

109
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:14,080
Then live as you wish.

110
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:16,200
You are the best, Father.

111
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:17,720
Come.

112
00:08:19,760 --> 00:08:22,620
I pay my respects to Your Highness and the Princess.

113
00:08:23,080 --> 00:08:24,210
Greetings, Mr. Jin.

114
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:27,200
Since you and Mr. Jin have important matters to discuss,

115
00:08:27,200 --> 00:08:28,760
I will take my leave now.

116
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:29,640
Go ahead.

117
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:33,640
Do not learn those rigid feminine virtues.

118
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:34,960
I understand.

119
00:08:38,120 --> 00:08:38,980
Your Highness,

120
00:08:39,039 --> 00:08:39,919
it's done.

121
00:08:40,679 --> 00:08:44,039
I have slipped a rare poison into Xie Wanshu's tea and snacks.

122
00:08:44,039 --> 00:08:45,720
Once he is emotionally agitated,

123
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:47,120
the poison will immediately

124
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:48,680
invade his blood and heart,

125
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:51,060
making him unable to speak

126
00:08:51,320 --> 00:08:52,680
and paralyzing his limbs.

127
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:53,520
Excellent.

128
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:55,570
These useless fools

129
00:08:56,640 --> 00:08:58,360
dared to expose me.

130
00:09:00,240 --> 00:09:02,880
The Xie father and son are the perfect scapegoats.

131
00:09:02,880 --> 00:09:03,810
It's just right.

132
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:06,010
Your Highness is truly brilliant.

133
00:09:06,040 --> 00:09:07,480
Xiao Jingyan managed to intercept

134
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:09,760
Xie Yuheng's secret letter colluding with the Northern Di.

135
00:09:09,760 --> 00:09:11,920
It was only a matter of time before he followed the clues to you,

136
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:13,580
I'm afraid it was inevitable.

137
00:09:13,880 --> 00:09:15,200
Speed is crucial in war.

138
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:18,060
By preemptively offering up the Xie father and son,

139
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:21,200
you not only cut off Xiao Jingyan's trail,

140
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:23,940
but also eliminated a traitor for the court.

141
00:09:24,080 --> 00:09:26,480
Killing two birds with one stone.

142
00:09:27,160 --> 00:09:28,320
When the Emperor hears of this,

143
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:30,520
he will surely praise your decisiveness

144
00:09:30,520 --> 00:09:31,380
and foresight.

145
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:33,880
He will commend you greatly.

146
00:09:49,560 --> 00:09:50,000
Heir.

147
00:09:50,560 --> 00:09:52,080
The target didn't take Heishui River.

148
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:53,080
We just received intel

149
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:54,960
that Xie Yuheng's supply convoy rerouted to Yaogu Road,

150
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:56,840
but he himself didn't follow.

151
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:00,960
Yaogu Road.

152
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:04,660
Our plan has been exposed.

153
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:09,170
This map of the Northern border defense left by my father

154
00:10:09,280 --> 00:10:10,610
has been tampered with.

155
00:10:15,760 --> 00:10:17,490
Tell the men to head back first.

156
00:10:26,800 --> 00:10:28,000
I thought Lord Xiao,

157
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:29,920
a brilliant strategist,

158
00:10:30,120 --> 00:10:32,520
had set an inescapable trap at Heishui River,

159
00:10:32,520 --> 00:10:35,040
so Xie Yuheng couldn't escape even with wings.

160
00:10:35,040 --> 00:10:35,640
In the end,

161
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:37,800
after waiting half the night,

162
00:10:37,800 --> 00:10:39,460
we haven't seen a single soul.

163
00:10:39,560 --> 00:10:42,020
Whoever is pulling the strings behind this,

164
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:44,760
I will definitely root them out.

165
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:56,160
Honorable envoy of Beidi.

166
00:11:00,800 --> 00:11:02,080
The time has come.

167
00:11:03,920 --> 00:11:05,050
It is time to send you

168
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:08,360
to meet the Wolf God.

169
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:22,850
Lord Xie.

170
00:11:26,320 --> 00:11:28,180
Why did the body of the Beidi envoy

171
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:31,520
appear in your Xie family's courtyard?

172
00:11:33,880 --> 00:11:36,810
The person was clearly killed by you, Your Highness.

173
00:11:37,920 --> 00:11:38,640
Xie Yuheng.

174
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:41,000
Open your dog eyes and see clearly.

175
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:43,880
The handwriting on this secret letter

176
00:11:43,880 --> 00:11:45,640
to the Right Wise King of Beidi,

177
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:49,000
and this glaring red cinnabar seal,

178
00:11:50,600 --> 00:11:53,660
this seems to be your Xie family's unique private seal.

179
00:11:55,040 --> 00:11:56,700
The evidence is irrefutable.

180
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,660
How will you defend yourself?

181
00:12:03,160 --> 00:12:05,360
If you don't want to implicate Master Xie,

182
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:06,280
I advise you

183
00:12:08,640 --> 00:12:09,520
to confess.

184
00:12:13,880 --> 00:12:17,010
It's the old fox teaching the young fox how to gnaw bones.

185
00:12:18,160 --> 00:12:19,040
I didn't expect

186
00:12:19,560 --> 00:12:21,960
such a good show late at night.

187
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:26,240
Xie Yuheng.

188
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:29,320
You should be heading to the northern border to transport supplies,

189
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:30,520
serving the country.

190
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:31,360
How come

191
00:12:31,720 --> 00:12:34,450
you've become the Prince of Ling's executioner?

192
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:36,000
Xiao Jingyan,

193
00:12:36,880 --> 00:12:39,520
stop talking nonsense and slandering me.

194
00:12:39,720 --> 00:12:40,560
Slandering?

195
00:12:41,280 --> 00:12:42,320
Three years ago,

196
00:12:42,640 --> 00:12:44,500
the stolen batch from the armory,

197
00:12:44,520 --> 00:12:47,600
black iron ingots enough to equip three thousand elite cavalry,

198
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:49,960
I'm afraid they are in Your Highness's shady furnaces,

199
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:51,220
burning day and night.

200
00:12:51,680 --> 00:12:53,880
I just wonder if this great asset of our country

201
00:12:53,880 --> 00:12:55,040
was forged into

202
00:12:55,880 --> 00:12:58,280
a sharp sword aimed at the border of Dafeng,

203
00:12:58,440 --> 00:12:59,640
or melted into

204
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:02,280
scimitars to honor the jackals of Beidi.

205
00:13:04,560 --> 00:13:06,960
What a great heir of the Marquis of Zhenbei.

206
00:13:07,160 --> 00:13:09,960
You think you can convict me with just empty words?

207
00:13:10,160 --> 00:13:11,520
Wishful thinking!

208
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:13,170
My Lord Heir,

209
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:15,050
you'd better first think about

210
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:18,120
how to clean up the mess of the Xie family's treason.

211
00:13:25,000 --> 00:13:25,720
Xie Yuheng,

212
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:28,610
it's perfect for you to take the blame.

213
00:13:29,400 --> 00:13:30,760
The solid proof of treason is here,

214
00:13:30,760 --> 00:13:31,890
caught red-handed.

215
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:34,730
You'd better stay well for your master

216
00:13:34,960 --> 00:13:36,690
in the cells of the Dali Temple.

217
00:13:37,680 --> 00:13:38,400
Qingshu!

218
00:13:40,520 --> 00:13:42,360
Qingshu, listen to me.

219
00:13:42,840 --> 00:13:44,800
I didn't set the fire at the Zhuque Tower,

220
00:13:44,800 --> 00:13:46,640
and I didn't kill the envoy of Beidi.

221
00:13:46,640 --> 00:13:48,000
It was all the Prince of Ling.

222
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:49,240
He was the one pulling the strings

223
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:50,240
to frame me!

224
00:13:50,960 --> 00:13:51,490
Qingshu,

225
00:13:51,800 --> 00:13:52,930
you must believe me!

226
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:55,300
You didn't set the fire yourself,

227
00:13:55,680 --> 00:13:57,840
and you didn't kill the envoy yourself,

228
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:59,640
but you truly betrayed me.

229
00:14:00,640 --> 00:14:01,300
Xie Yuheng,

230
00:14:02,120 --> 00:14:03,380
the blood on your hands

231
00:14:03,720 --> 00:14:05,000
is no less.

232
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,040
Take him away.

233
00:14:09,360 --> 00:14:10,040
Qingshu!

234
00:14:10,360 --> 00:14:10,960
Qingshu!

235
00:14:11,520 --> 00:14:12,480
Qingshu!

236
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:17,160
Xiao Jingyan,

237
00:14:18,040 --> 00:14:18,920
the trap you carefully laid three days ago

238
00:14:18,920 --> 00:14:22,000
for the Xie father and son

239
00:14:22,520 --> 00:14:23,380
has completely

240
00:14:23,680 --> 00:14:25,680
fallen through today.

241
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:27,060
A change in the plan

242
00:14:27,640 --> 00:14:28,970
might not be a bad thing.

243
00:14:29,880 --> 00:14:30,940
Beneath the waves,

244
00:14:31,600 --> 00:14:34,360
a big fish might be hiding.

245
00:14:35,560 --> 00:14:38,280
We might as well wait and see.

246
00:15:09,360 --> 00:15:10,120
Cuimei

247
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:10,760
Cuimei

248
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:12,520
Yong

249
00:15:13,240 --> 00:15:13,760
Huachao

250
00:15:13,760 --> 00:15:14,720
Weikun Huachao

251
00:15:16,880 --> 00:15:18,560
Long Cong Biao Hao

252
00:15:21,320 --> 00:15:21,920
Shuang Bin

253
00:15:21,920 --> 00:15:22,560
Shuang Bin

254
00:15:22,520 --> 00:15:23,520
Ning Zheng

255
00:15:25,920 --> 00:15:27,920
Hao Chun Kang Shuai Hua

256
00:15:31,480 --> 00:15:31,560
Wei Chao

257
00:15:31,560 --> 00:15:32,040
Wei Chao

258
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:34,240
Qiang Yuan Liang Bo

259
00:15:34,240 --> 00:15:35,300
Qiang Yuan Liang Bo

260
00:15:49,800 --> 00:15:50,360
Xi

261
00:15:51,760 --> 00:15:52,520
Xi

262
00:15:52,520 --> 00:15:53,280
Tao Qiang

263
00:15:57,080 --> 00:15:58,560
Hui Yue Yun Qing

264
00:16:02,040 --> 00:16:02,560
Yi Yi

265
00:16:02,680 --> 00:16:03,160
Yi Yi
